<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nṣyb ạ̉hl ạldnyạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- naṣību ạảh̊li ạldũn̊yā
 fī hadẖihi ạl̊ḥayāh̊
 yūāṣilūna ạlsãʿ̊yā
 naḥ̊wa ạl̊gẖinay̱ wāl̊jāh̊

[V2]
 2- ạảmãạ ạảnā fafakẖ̊rī
 biạlrãbĩ lạ siwāh̊
 wabiạltũqay̱ wāl̊birĩ
 ạản̊ẓuru waj̊ha ạllh̊

[V3]
 3- waʿin̊damā ạảqūmu
 ạủʿāyinu ạlại̹lah̊
 wamaʿahu ạảdūmu
 ạảsẖ̊baʿu min̊ mar̊ậh̊

[V4]
 4- fālsẖũk̊ru lil̊ḥabībi
 ại̹lay̱ maday̱ ạldũhūr̊
 ʿizĩy kan̊zī naṣībī
 wamun̊tahay̱ ạlsũrūr̊</lyrics>
</song>